msgstr "**Agissons maintenant !** [](https://rebellion.global/groups/#countries)[](/get-involved/)\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-08-31-act-now-extinction-rebellion-demands.md:72
msgid ""
"[Join the rebellion](https://rebellion.global/get-involved/){.xr-button}"
msgstr "[Rejoignez-nous !](https://rebellion.global/get-involved/){.xr-button}"
